const Create = () => {
    
    return(
        <section className="profile_undergrad profile_section">
            <label>
                University name
                <select>
                    <option value={1}>Emory Univeristy</option>
                </select>
            </label>

            <label>
                GPA
                <select>
                    <option value={1}>4.0</option>
                </select>
            </label>

            <label>

                <input type="text" />
            </label>

            <label>
                Major(s)
                <input type="text" />
            </label>

            <label>

                <input type="text" />
            </label>

            <label>
                Program Name
                <input type="text" />
            </label>

            <label className="textarea">
                Activities
                <textarea type="text" />
            </label>

            <label>
                Volunteer Experience
                <textarea type="text"/>
            </label>
        </section>
    ); 

}

export default Create;
